Name

qt_dictionary_destroy - deallocate a concurrent dictionary

Synopsis

#include <qthread/dictionary.h>

void
qt_dictionary_destroy (qt_dictionary *d);

Description

This function deallocates the dictionary data structure d.Theembeddedtagcleanupfunctionwillbecalledforalltagsremaininginthedictionary.
